that we can welcome

00:00:10.400 --> 00:00:13.290
Doctor John Gottman and
Doctor Julie Schwartz Gottman

00:00:13.290 --> 00:00:15.340
here today.

00:00:15.340 --> 00:00:18.026
So, thank you so much
for joining us at Google.

00:00:18.026 --> 00:00:19.150
We're thrilled to have you.

00:00:19.150 --> 00:00:20.816
I've been a fan of
yours for many years,

00:00:20.816 --> 00:00:22.442
