So, first we have
Doctor John Gottman.

00:00:37.070 --> 00:00:40.110
He is world renowned for his
work on marital stability

00:00:40.110 --> 00:00:41.890
and divorce prediction.

00:00:41.890 --> 00:00:44.210
He's conducted forty years
of breakthrough research

00:00:44.210 --> 00:00:46.120
with thousands of couples.

00:00:46.120 --> 00:00:49.830
He was recognized as one of
the top 10 most influential

00:00:49.830 --> 00:00:51.455
therapists of the
