00:47:32.635 --> 00:47:36.220
through some difficult times.

00:47:36.220 --> 00:47:40.154
JULIE GOTTMAN: On
the other hand,

00:47:40.154 --> 00:47:45.790
one has to be pretty careful in
terms-- I've done a lot of work

00:47:45.790 --> 00:47:51.040
with arranged marriages as
