00:54:14.740 --> 00:54:17.360
Good enough, right?

00:54:17.360 --> 00:54:19.470
So that doesn't mean perfect.

00:54:19.470 --> 00:54:23.550
Nobody really gets
away in their marriage

00:54:23.550 --> 00:54:27.470
without having the incidents of
being critical, or defensive,

00:54:27.470 --> 00:54:30.920
or even contemptuous, whatever.

00:54:30.920 --> 00:54:35.540
We all will slide into
that from time to time.

00:54:35.540 --> 00:54:39.670
This is a very critical
culture we've grown up in,

00:54:39.670 --> 00:54:41.620
so we come by it righteously.

00:54:41.620 --> 00:54:45.090
We know where criticism
looks like, most of us.

00:54:45.090 --> 00:54:48.730
And so it comes trippingly
to the tongue when

00:54:48.730 --> 00:54:50.410
we're angry about something.

